1.2
log
@We do not hardcode /usr/local.
@
text
@d3 1
a3 1
# $OpenBSD: polipo.rc,v 1.1 2010/11/11 20:19:52 kili Exp $
d9 1
a9 4

rc_reload() {
	rc_err "$0: reload is not supported"
}
@


